<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-2325] @Produce - Causes BeanInvocation to be kept as Body which causes problem with subsequent bean invocations</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-2325</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The route&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    &amp;lt;camelContext id=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;camel&quot;&lt;/span&gt; trace=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; xmlns=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;http:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//camel.apache.org/schema/spring&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;        &amp;lt;route&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;from uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;direct:start&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;to uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;log:foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;split&amp;gt;
                &amp;lt;method bean=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;cool&quot;&lt;/span&gt; method=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;split&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
                &amp;lt;transform&amp;gt;&amp;lt;simple&amp;gt;Hello ${body}&amp;lt;/simple&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/transform&amp;gt;
                &amp;lt;to uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;mock:split&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;/split&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/route&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/camelContext&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is caused problem when a @Produce bean is used to send a message to the route.&lt;br/&gt;
2010-01-01 18:07:43,720 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;main           &amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ERROR DefaultErrorHandler            - Failed delivery for exchangeId: b7098680-4a16-4289-bdf4-3197b0b37aea. Exhausted after delivery attempt: 1 caught: org.apache.camel.language.bean.RuntimeBeanExpressionException: Failed to invoke method: split on cool due to: org.apache.camel.RuntimeCamelException: java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: object is not an instance of declaring class&lt;/p&gt;</description>
